My stance is this; if its a group of players who will actually use the stuff (Iksar Regen BP-great shaman piece, Hnagmans noose, Traks tooth, etc) then fine, I mean after all thats what its there for...but when I see two or three very high level high powered players sitting in TT on their butts hitting the rares cycle I shake my head. I mean at that point they are simply spending real time in a game played for fun farming crap they wont wear or use...for what reason? To amass some virtual money in their virtual bank? To maybe equip twinks? To feel like they accomplished something?<br>
