<br>
Clan B found the Tower of Frozen Shadow. Rarely has more that 10 people in it and commonly only has 2-6. We liked the Tower and spent about a month and a half there. We learned all the secrets of floors 1-6a and had a grand time of it. Some pretty nice drops (with horrid ac on them) are in the Tower. Anyone who knows the ToFS knows that tis not a normal camp check. Being polite means to ask for a Floor Check and try to avoid the floor others are on.<br>
<br>
We were stuck on 4 for quite some time, at one point. We were gettin the Prophecy Scroll and Sorcerer's Cup for our casters &amp; healers.  It was late one nite, when 4 of us finally got Amon to spawn. Excited, we sent our monk o'er to Cara to see what she had as soon as Amon was dead. Our monk practically shouted in /g-say that she had the Cup in her hand. We invised and ran like mad o'er there, our guild magi in tow. We got there and paused to take a pic of her and her cup with our magi standin next to her. Just at that moment, I came vis. I was attacked, so immediatly our monk started hammerin away at Cara.<br>
<br>
Next thing I see in /g-say is our monk shoutin that we were bein KS-d. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Never really having encountered this, I didn't know what to do, so I started nuking. I wasn't fast enough, neither was our magi. Our Cara spawn was promptly slaughtered and the cup looted. Within minutes, our KS-er UN-Friend zoned to 5th floor and disappeared. Side note: Previous to this, the magi that KSed us was in /ooc doin floor check and random bs talkin with us. I could show ya snip-its from pics takin, but as the GM says... ya can doctor those to say anything ya want. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I'll spare ya the story of talkin to a GM and havin a GM tell me to work it out with the magi that KSed us. Supposedly the Magi turned it around and accused US of KSin HIM. Because of spending a lot of time in Norrath protecting the image of Clan B, we were believed... but nothin could be done.<br>
<br>
Anyway, after such a long time in the ToFS, it was a great let down to us. This was the very first time we had gotten Cara to drop the cup for us. The mood and spirit of a great group was gone and noone really wanted to stay. We camped out for the nite with near-tears in our eyes.<br>
<br>
The next day, we logged on and again tried for the couple of pieces our guildmates needed &amp; wanted. For some unknown reason, Cara kept spawnin all o'er the place and dropped 2 cups during the day!!!!!<br>
<br>
We got our payback, tis for sure. But I still remember the sadness of the group when they realized that sometimes a lot of hard work can disappear in less than 30 seconds.<br>
<br>
I, and most of Clan B, play this game for fun and comradarie. Not for Uber loot or Uber levels. Usually, if we see somethin camped, we walk away. /shrug... I guess not everyone can be polite... or even try, Tychor. All we can do is continue to play our game our own way and patiently wait for a cute payback. Like Cara droppin 2 cups for us in 1 day. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
